Excellent dumpling place! Decent price, good for takeouts and eating in.

在醋瓶里應該有唔少蟲，蚊滋仔。叫左一碗麵線和鍋貼，倒醋的時候卻發現倒左少少醋，隻碟仔已經起碼有4隻蚊滋仔，當下立即同店員反映。反映後，罪證已被極速收走，連相都影唔切，無作出任何道歉和補救措施。店員默默行開了，把余下醋倒了便算。
我之前亦把醋倒入麵線，同樣發現被加料。
希望店員要注意衛生，其他客人加醋的時後亦要留意。大家想補充蛋白質就俾錢吃了
晚餐 方便快捷

reviews.text: Good food court with low prices. Nice interior
Medium sized shopping mall and home
Many food restaurants, but the toilet is dirty
Nice unusual mall. Mainly on ground floor with some old Hong Kong style parts. Food places, bubble tea, kids playhouse, supermarket, all available here on rather small area.

It's not a bad place to visit but need to sort out the public toilets & people who works at the back of the building smoking.
If they can add baby changing room event better.
